data.text: @Babs_Bunny420 I am so happy to hear another Gaga fan say this. I am happy for her and she looks so beautiful but...I just can't catch hype
I'm so proud of Gaga. She deserves all the praise but I honestly have no hype for A Star Is Born... other than all the Gaga solos on the soundtrack.
And other than Rocket Raccoon, I don't even like Bradley Cooper. https://t.co/AyJ7QgWCpr
